FlyGym Tracker -- per-vial Drosophila locomotor-activity tracker for the FlyGym v2
rotating IR-silhouette rig.

This software is provided to authorised users of the FlyGym rig. No permission is
granted to copy, modify, distribute, or create derivative works, except as agreed
in writing with the copyright holder.

THIS PLACEHOLDER IS THE CONSERVATIVE DEFAULT, NOT A CONSIDERED CHOICE. It was set
to "all rights reserved" because that is the reversible option: software can be
released under an open licence later, but a licence once granted cannot be
withdrawn from copies already distributed. If this is to be shipped to customers,
or published, replace this file with the licence you actually intend -- an
academic-use licence, MIT, GPL, or a commercial EULA -- before distributing it.

