THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

The installed application bundles the following, each under its own licence:

    Python              PSF License Agreement
    PySide6 / Qt        LGPL v3
    OpenCV              Apache License 2.0
    NumPy               BSD 3-Clause
    pandas              BSD 3-Clause
    PyYAML              MIT
    openpyxl            MIT

Qt is used under the LGPL. The LGPL requires that users be able to replace the Qt
libraries with their own build. This application is distributed with Qt as
separate, unmodified dynamic libraries in the installation directory, which
satisfies that requirement; Qt itself is not modified.

The HikRobot MVS SDK is NOT bundled and NOT redistributed. It is installed
separately by the operator, direct from HikRobot, under HikRobot's own licence.
